data.description: Welcome to desirable Plantation Oaks subdivision.  This 4/ 2.5 gem is nestled on a peaceful cul-de-sac.  Step inside and you are greeted with beautiful tile flooring throughout the main areas. The kitchen is a true delight, featuring a 5-burner gas range, microwave, dishwasher, instant hot water dispenser, water softener and walk-in pantry.  You'll appreciate the recently added covered porch perfect for savoring your morning coffee or hosting memorable gatherings in the evening.  Updates to the property include a roof (6/15 with WPI-8 certificate), Hardi plank siding, 2nd floor HVAC system, LED lighting, smart Nest C0/smoke detectors and digital thermostats.  Upper back deck built in 2020, siding replaced 8/20 with WPI-8,Dishwasher 2018. both side fences updated Lake Jackson offers recreational activities, including fishing&boating, & is home to the Lake Jackson Historical Museum.Call today!
